		   <table class="mform"  border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" width="100%" >
		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">Dispelling the charisma myth<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: Dispelling the charisma myth";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Sat, Nov 10th 7:49 PM2001 </span><span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/db/classes.html?class=4&mid=100543975354570&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=4&mid=100543975354570&num=11&page=0&post=1&replyto=100543975354570"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=100543975354570></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span class="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=608"><span id="Scholar">Nexroth</span></a><b><span id="Scholar"><br>Scholar</span></b><br />28 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Default [2.24]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Nexroth&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>I just wanted to save a lot of people from the silly idea of making an effort to increase their bard's charisma.&nbsp;&nbsp;I see far too many people claiming how important charisma is when it actually isn't very important at all. <br /> <br />Charisma supposedly makes charm & mesmerize songs more effective, but the increase is so tiny that it's negligible.  Even an increase from 110 to 200 charisma won't be noticed. <br /> <br />The best thing you can do for levels under 45 is wear as much AC gear as possible, and keep your instrument skills at their maximum.  After 45 you'll want to start considering more resistance gear and things to increase hp/sta. <br /> <br />Don't even worry about charisma until you have pixie strike.  Then just keep it above 100 and you'll be fine.  Don't waste your money on every +cha item you can find.  You'll only be making yourself weaker. <br /> <br />Nexroth <br />Virtuoso of the Bloods Guard <br />Maker of Many Fine Things <br />Cazic-Thule server</p>
</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >11 Replies</td></tr></table>
